    {
      "index": 12,
      "type": "content",
      "title": "第 7 页",
      "audio": "assets/ppt/audio/ppt_3.mp3",
      "subtitles": [
        {
          "at": 0.1,
          "text": "The modal particle “吧” is used at the end of a question to express a tone of conjecture or estimation."
        },
        {
          "at": 8,
          "text": "Basically, when you use “吧” in a question, you are making a guess that you are fairly confident about, and you are asking the other person to confirm it."
        },
        {
          "at": 18,
          "text": "Here are some examples:你们就是她的学生吧？她唱歌很好听吧？"
        }
      ],
